1177
01:49:03,044 --> 01:49:04,511
Why not?!

1178
01:49:11,019 --> 01:49:12,884
Gotcha!

1179
01:49:16,591 --> 01:49:17,990
Where are they?

1180
01:49:29,471 --> 01:49:30,904
Gotcha!

1181
01:49:47,856 --> 01:49:48,982
Miss Yamaguchi!

1182
01:50:03,838 --> 01:50:05,066
Gotcha!

1183
01:50:22,757 --> 01:50:23,746
Yankumi.

1184
01:50:24,926 --> 01:50:26,086
Thanks.

1185
01:50:26,327 --> 01:50:27,521
What?

1186
01:50:28,363 --> 01:50:29,625
Nothing.

1187
01:50:31,966 --> 01:50:33,194
Odagiri.

1188
01:50:35,303 --> 01:50:40,832
If anything's troubling you,
come back anytime.

1189
01:50:44,679 --> 01:50:50,345
I'm your teacher until I die.

1190
